title: #118: China's One Belt, One Road with Punch Drunk's Johnny Woodard
description: Welcome to another truth bomb episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  On this episode, the guys welcome from Punch Drunk Sports, Johnny Woodard to discuss China's attempt to jack the United States' swag.  This is one of my favorite episodes that we have ever done, so I hope you enjoy listening.  Thank you for all of your support.
